slaves_df = []

dir_path = r'msi-ge62-val/'
for filename in np.sort(os.listdir(dir_path)):
    if filename.endswith(".csv"):
        print(dir_path + filename)
        df = pd.read_csv(dir_path + filename)
        slaves_df.append(df)

name_to_index = {}
for i in range(len(list_row)):
    name_to_index[total_data['Metric'][i]] = i
    
def get_plot_data(index):
    print([total_data.iloc[index][str(i) + '_slave'] for i in range(1,SLAVES_NB + 1)])
    return [float(total_data.iloc[index][str(i) + '_slave']) for i in range(1,SLAVES_NB + 1)]
